beer.beer_description:
Motueka/Kohia Nelson/Citra

This was meant to be a tap exclusive release but as we kept drinking it we decided it was too good to not can. So, spoiler alert, it will be in the next tin release. Get a taste of it early on tap at the taproom!

Our second beer playing around with Freestyle Hops' Kohia Nelson. We fed some to our friendly Digestibot, and their verdict..."Yum Yum". ?
